   9      pounds        goose -- rinsed, patted dry
   2      teaspoons     salt
   8      ounces        herb-seasoned stuffing cubes
   1 1/2  cups          water
     1/2  cup           brandy
     1/4  pound         butter -- (1 stick)
   2                    tangerines, peeled, sectioned
   1      stalk         celery -- thinly sliced
     3/4  cup           pitted prunes -- quartered
