                           Garry's Mexican Rice

Recipe By     : Garry Howard
Serving Size  : 4    Preparation Time :0:00
Categories    : Bbq List                         Sides

  Amount  Measure       Ingredient -- Preparation Method
--------  ------------  --------------------------------
   1      tablespoon    oil
