   1      tablespoon    oil
   2      pounds        chicken breasts boneless
   2                    onions
   2      teaspoons     minced garlic
   1      teaspoon      oregano
   1      teaspoon      cumin powder
   2      teaspoons     ground red chile
   1      tablespoon    red chile flakes
   1                    tomato
   1      can           tomatillos
   4      pounds        green chilies
   4      cups          Wyler's chicken bouillon
